r a way to extend their short life spans.","genre_ids":[878,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.05,"vote_count":14715,"poster_path":"/63N9uy8nd9j7Eog2axPQ8lbr3Wj.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-25","vote_average":7.94,"backdrop_path":"/hJ5R9d6QuH3tzr8L8neZZTuzNXm.jpg","original_title":"Blade Runner","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":1459256,"adult":false,"title":"All at Once","video":false,"overview":"On a journey across Central Park, an introspective high school senior develops unexpected feelings for her charismatic co-valedictorian as they discuss love, family, and their futures.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1254,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/agR17MkooVNSfbdbEH1vS0PboJd.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-08","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/uqTyqeNF9g2A6wYEXWmXqnbxgRi.jpg","original_title":"All at Once","original_language":"en"},{"id":661653,"adult":false,"title":"Oliverio and the Pool","video":false,"overview":"When something unexpected happens in Oliverio’s family, all he wants to do is walk away. He settles on a deckchair by the pool and decides there is no reason to move. Life swirls around him, revealing secrets and presenting new challenges. Through moments of death, excrement and basic physics, Oliverio learns that some truths cannot be ignored.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":0.2066,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/nJlTuSCvg6GuI5Y21xN2cF9tzhT.jpg","release_date":"2022-02-03","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/kpfOgz6u1AySqZTvMjfcod8NTcu.jpg","original_title":"Oliverio y la piscina","original_language":"es"},{"id":8587,"adult":false,"title":"The Lion King","video":false,"overview":"Young lion prince Simba, eager to one day become king of the Pride Lands, grows up under the watchful eye of his father Mufasa; all the while his villainous uncle Scar conspires to take the throne for himself. Amid betrayal and tragedy, Simba must confront his past and find his rightful place in the Circle of Life.","genre_ids":[10751,16,18,12],"popularity":17.1511,"vote_count":19408,"poster_path":"/sKCr78MXSLixwmZ8DyJLrpMsd15.jpg","release_date":"1994-06-15","vote_average":8.252,"backdrop_path":"/6GF9uJs7AnbcJvyfoZyjZv063Oo.jpg","original_title":"The Lion King","original_language":"en"},{"id":661674,"adult":false,"title":"Howard","video":false,"overview":"Howard Mitchell is a responsible young man who will soon be graduating from high school. He works at Resnick's Pharmacy to be able to earn enough money to put himself through college. But in part because of the life lessons he learns from Mr. Resnick through Mr. Resnick's somewhat cynical observations of the customers that come into the pharmacy, Howard is intrigued by an offer from George, his best friend, to tour Canada following their graduation instead of going directly into a post-secondary institution. This trip would not be a vacation, but rather an opportunity to see what life has to offer by meeting people from different parts of the country, while they work odd jobs along the way. This idea goes against the sensibilities of Howard's parents and Howard's girlfriend, Mary, who see this trip as just another impetuously stupid idea by flaky George. Howard has to try and reconcile all these competing forces in his life.  —Huggo","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4084,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1957-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Howard","original_language":"en"},{"id":277369,"adult":false,"title":"Hail, Hero!","video":false,"overview":"Carl Dixon decides to quit school and enlist in the Army, even though he's already run afoul of the law as a Vietnam protestor. It is our hero's intention to use love, rather than bullets, to combat the Viet Cong. Needless to say, his idealism is no match for the harsher realities of war.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2319,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/kyhiTr5YiNg2d5lrLyXrq4KsICi.jpg","release_date":"1969-10-04","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/mQtq4Ajct42GvbAcXrGPdXx3es7.jpg","original_title":"Hail, Hero!","original_language":"en"},{"id":1067485,"adult":false,"title":"Sebastian","video":false,"overview":"Max is a 25-year-old freelance writer and aspiring novelist who seems well on his way to success in London’s cultural spheres. Yet by night, he finds a different kind of exhilaration as a sex worker with the pseudonym Sebastian, meeting men via an escorting platform. Max uses his experiences as Sebastian to fuel his stories and the worthy debut novel that he has been longing to write, finally seems within reach.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.2755,"vote_count":47,"poster_path":"/22JTGme2MLETmvhHQdiKP78S5Qf.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-02","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/kEvBFfqCtJvtvwZcrprAT3dSvij.jpg","original_title":"Sebastian","original_language":"en"},{"id":470861,"adult":false,"title":"Liza, Liza, Skies Are Grey","video":false,"overview":"A teenage girl and her boyfriend set off on an eventful road trip up the coast of California hoping to figure out the meaning of love and life.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.4886,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/54XDVjXruiusiTKLIMzNr1q89C.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-17","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/lbYjniPOnwdPXFpw4gOQ0VwzgiW.jpg","original_title":"Liza, Liza, Skies Are Grey","original_language":"en"},{"id":470901,"adult":false,"title":"Face 2 Face","video":false,"overview":"Over a series of video chats, a teenage outcast reaches out to his childhood friend, but finds that behind the veneer of popularity and a seemingly perfect life, she hides a disturbing secret.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3045,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/lciZWx3qVPUxGnw9rzNBqNgQPuN.jpg","release_date":"2017-04-23","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/9VoU9AV6POqPSVXVR832BZDBAr.jpg","original_title":"Face 2 Face","original_language":"en"},{"id":661781,"adult":false,"title":"Heatwave","video":false,"overview":"The tense relationship between a mother and son reaches a climax during a summer heatwave.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.6913,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/qdecMfnbQhs186tzJD0FlrurzhA.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-21","vote_average":1,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Heatwave","original_language":"en"},{"id":8967,"adult":false,"title":"The Tree of Life","video":false,"overview":"The impressionistic story of a Texas family in the 1950s. The film follows the life journey of the eldest son, Jack, through the innocence of childhood to his disillusioned adult years as he tries to reconcile a complicated relationship with his father. Jack finds himself a lost soul in the modern world, seeking answers to the origins and meaning of life while questioning the existence of faith.","genre_ids":[18,14],"popularity":2.946,"vote_count":3278,"poster_path":"/l8cwuB5WJSoj4uMAsnzuHBOMaSJ.jpg","release_date":"2011-05-17","vote_average":6.727,"backdrop_path":"/xq1HIwZq9VbuvMQELAua1nqEkH.jpg","original_title":"The Tree of Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":8992,"adult":false,"title":"The Sure Thing","video":false,"overview":"Gib, a beer-guzzling slob, and Alison, an uptight Ivy-Leaguer, are an unlikely duo stuck together on a cross-country trip during Christmas break. At first they get on each other's nerves but, as time passes, they find their divergent natures complement each other. Now they need to realize what they've already found before it's too late.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":1.6926,"vote_count":314,"poster_path":"/a9cuohQn5kczi4htWZAZjEZvXkZ.jpg","release_date":"1985-03-01","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/aTiarj2HriXg3EQROAuyRvHlf0V.jpg","original_title":"The Sure Thing","original_language":"en"},{"id":8915,"adult":false,"title":"Amelia","video":false,"overview":"A look at the life of legendary American pilot Amelia Earhart, who disappeared while flying over the Pacific Ocean in 1937 in an attempt to make a flight around the world.","genre_ids":[12,18,36],"popularity":0.97,"vote_count":252,"poster_path":"/4c7QMp7JZl70K8x5oJuY40mckW